posts.post_content:
Hello
I've got a large number of PSA graded T207s available. This post is for ones with Recruit advertising backs. Front/back scans available at links. Open to offers. Items are also for sale on my website. Direct purchase on website trumps other offers, I'll take it trumps ongoing negotiations. Prices assume PayPal G/S and include shipping.

See other post for other backs: [url]https://www.net54baseball.com/showthread.php?t=333037[/url]

PMs or emails to [url]burl@burlssports.com[/url]
